divs: Sighting DetailsOut walking my dog, noticed what I thought was a very bright star, went inside to get my golf scope so I could see what it was, after getting a better look I got very excited so I went inside to get my wife so she too could see what I was seeing...she was not convinced it was a UFO but I stood there and watched the lights pulsate and then...it was gone!!! After about 20 minutes, it just POOF, disappeared!!
Summary: Craft hovered, lights pulsated and then it just disappeared within a blink of the eye.
